name: Ben
text: whuh- where?? how did I get here??

name: Ben
text: Looks like its jammed or something...What happened...All I remember is stealing that....oh god

name: Ben
text: Im not sure why...but I feel like I should find a way to get that elevator working before this watch gets to 12..

name: Notes
text: to the next poor soul who ends up here. Sweep. I don't know why but it fixed that rickety elevator

name: Ben
text: woah, what the heck are you?

name: DustBunny
text: oh s-sorry to alarm you...m-my name is dustin the the dust bunny.

name: Ben
text: no its alright I just didnt know anyone or...i guess anything was in here...do you know where I am??

name: DustBunny
text: oh uh...I dont think I can tell you..Im sorry I wish I could help but it will end the same as it did for all the others....

name: Ben
text: what. what do you mean??? What others??? Did one of those 'others' write that note I found?

name: DustBunny
text: ive said too much, im sorry

name: Ben
text: Its okay, if you arent going to talk can you atleast help me sweep?

name: Ben
text: oh my god what have I done

name: Ben
text: oh uh...no time to think about that I guess, sounds like the elevator is working again and im not taking any chances by waiting
